10311%2FVPEAPPHELVGHBFVLNP3TNVVILU%2F&h=50d62edc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/VPEAPPHELVGHBFVLNP3TNVVILU/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"投左共 投中間"},{"pid":"780d903ae24cb637c959d8341689199301544cb9","tid":2442400,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:03:15.000Z","msg":"喂新思維呢？滅咗黨嗱？<br />\n又想起個新朵搵錢 呃得到邊個啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f322ec69819aeea869c72d4c72d3a47bb7c4ff","tid":2442400,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20160228/s00001/【短片-新東補選】與梁天琦短兵相接-黃成智-唔係我哋努力爭取-你有鬼大學讀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20160228%2Fs00001%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E8%88%87%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E7%9F%AD%E5%85%B5%E7%9B%B8%E6%8E%A5-%E9%BB%83%E6%88%90%E6%99%BA-%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E9%AC%BC%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E8%AE%80&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=1e2cb00a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20160228%2Fs00001%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E8%88%87%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E7%9F%AD%E5%85%B5%E7%9B%B8%E6%8E%A5-%E9%BB%83%E6%88%90%E6%99%BA-%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E9%AC%BC%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E8%AE%80&h=dd5e41fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20160228/s00001/【短片-新東補選】與梁天琦短兵相接-黃成智-唔係我哋努力爭取-你有鬼大學讀</a><br />\n又要回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\